Bo has many friends.

481
00:29:39,577 --> 00:29:42,546
DUTCH^
He was the best...smart.

482
00:29:42,580 --> 00:29:45,071
l never had to tell Bo
to do anything twice.

483
00:29:45,116 --> 00:29:47,607
l would say it one time,
and bang, it was done...

484
00:29:47,652 --> 00:29:49,119
and it was done right.

485
00:29:49,154 --> 00:29:50,382
Hey, anybody in there?

486
00:29:50,421 --> 00:29:52,912
l promise you, kid,
it was done right.

487
00:29:52,957 --> 00:29:54,754
<i>You get high marks for this.</i>

488
00:29:54,793 --> 00:29:56,590
<i>lRVlNG: The fire inspector.</i>
<i>Must be payday.</i>

489
00:29:56,628 --> 00:29:58,289
l'll talk to him.

490
00:29:58,329 --> 00:29:59,694
Come on, open up!

491
00:29:59,731 --> 00:30:02,291
He had balls.
Nobody had balls like Bo.

492
00:30:02,333 --> 00:30:03,300
Let me talk to the manager.

493
00:30:03,334 --> 00:30:04,596
He's not here.
Come back later.

494
00:30:04,636 --> 00:30:08,163
l remember one time,
the guineas wanted him...

495
00:30:08,206 --> 00:30:11,733
to take out one of their guys,
and you know what he done?

496
00:30:11,776 --> 00:30:13,744
<i>He put on a cop's uniform.</i>

497
00:30:13,778 --> 00:30:14,836
Where's the manager?

498
00:30:14,879 --> 00:30:16,608
Hey, where you going?
You can't come in here.

499
00:30:16,648 --> 00:30:17,910
This is a private meeting.

500
00:30:17,949 --> 00:30:20,247
What's the matter, pal?
You got a problem, huh?

501
00:30:20,285 --> 00:30:22,685
[Screaming]

502
00:30:26,157 --> 00:30:28,125
You want a payoff, huh?!

503
00:30:31,529 --> 00:30:34,498
