a new pair of pants...

535
00:32:27,512 --> 00:32:29,810
a nice jacket,
shirt with a tie...

536
00:32:29,847 --> 00:32:31,576
pair of shoes with laces.

537
00:32:31,616 --> 00:32:33,550
lt's a personal
embarrassment to me...

538
00:32:33,584 --> 00:32:35,051
to see the way you dress.

539
00:32:35,086 --> 00:32:38,385
And l want you to get a valise
to put the clothes in.

540
00:32:38,423 --> 00:32:40,050
