613
00:38:02,446 --> 00:38:05,313
[Ship's engine chugging]

614
00:38:18,195 --> 00:38:21,289
Kid, go see what he's doing.

615
00:38:21,332 --> 00:38:23,960
He don't have no respect.
Go see if she's all right.

616
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:29,230
<i>BO: Do what l told you.</i>
<i>Go see if she's all right.</i>

617
00:38:38,949 --> 00:38:41,884
<i>DUTCH: You know what</i>
<i>l'm talking about, don't you?</i>

618
00:38:41,919 --> 00:38:46,015
Hmm? You don't care about
what's dead, do you?

619
00:38:46,057 --> 00:38:47,718
