l'm telling you right now...

620
00:38:47,758 --> 00:38:50,625
except for a few details,
he's dead.

621
00:38:50,661 --> 00:38:52,925
<i>Can you understand that?</i>

622
00:38:52,963 --> 00:38:54,692
[Sighs]

623
00:38:54,732 --> 00:38:57,758
You can forget about the dead,
can't you?

624
00:38:59,770 --> 00:39:03,206
<i>l think you've forgotten</i>
<i>already, haven't you?</i>

625
00:39:06,143 --> 00:39:08,202
<i>Well?</i>

626
00:39:10,748 --> 00:39:12,716
l'm waiting.

627
00:39:16,253 --> 00:39:19,222
lt's either a yes or a no.

628
00:39:21,392 --> 00:39:25,055
-l--l...
-What?

629
00:39:25,096 --> 00:39:28,224
DUTCH^
l'm sorry. l can't hear you.

