00:39:31,569 --> 00:39:34,470
[Sighs]

632
00:39:34,505 --> 00:39:35,802
Yes.

633
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:39,640
Aw...that's too bad.

634
00:39:39,677 --> 00:39:42,237
That's too bad for Bo.

