to begin with...

668
00:42:36,153 --> 00:42:37,620
if l'm not mistaken.

669
00:42:37,655 --> 00:42:39,555
<i>DREW: Darling, you'll just</i>
<i>have to make excuses for me.</i>

670
00:42:39,590 --> 00:42:41,854
HARVEY^ There's certain
proprieties to be maintained.

671
00:42:41,892 --> 00:42:44,383
You are my wife...
or have you forgotten?

672
00:42:44,428 --> 00:42:47,192
Harvey, what's the point
of making a fuss?

673
00:42:47,231 --> 00:42:48,528
There's a certain limit.

674
00:42:48,566 --> 00:42:50,193
