675
00:42:50,234 --> 00:42:51,565
but sooner or later,
you'll get in over your head...

676
00:42:51,602 --> 00:42:53,126
and then what will you do?

677
00:42:53,170 --> 00:42:55,968
Expect you to come
to the rescue like always.

678
00:42:56,006 --> 00:42:57,064
