680
00:43:00,978 --> 00:43:02,206
[Ring]

681
00:43:02,246 --> 00:43:04,942
lf that's my gangster,
tell him to wait.

682
00:43:08,986 --> 00:43:10,180
[Dutch strikes match]

683
